# Asset registry — {{COMPANY_NAME}}

Pointers to canonical asset files. The orchestrator holds the
**registry**, not the assets themselves (except small, git-diffable
ones — see "Local assets" below).

> When an asset version changes (logo refresh, icon redo), bump
> the version + date below. Old version stays referenced for
> historical assets in shipped artifacts.

