## Discipline

- Update this file when an asset version changes.
- An asset isn't "shipped" until it's listed here with a canonical
  pointer.
- If a sub-project needs an asset, point them at this file (not at
  a stale Slack message).
- When an asset is deprecated, mark it `deprecated` here with the
  successor referenced — don't delete history.

